{{Infobox sportsperson | name = Antonio Ahumada | image = | imagesize = | caption = | birth_name = | fullname = | nickname = | nationality = | residence = | birth_date = | birth_place = | death_date = | death_place = | height = | weight = | website = | country = | sport = [[Fencing]] | event = | collegeteam = | club = | team = | turnedpro = | coach = | retired = | coaching = | worlds = | regionals = | nationals = | olympics = | paralympics = | highestranking = | pb = | show-medals = yes }}
'''Antonio Ahumada''' was a Colombian [[fencing|fencer]]. He competed in the individual [[épée]] event at the [[1948 Summer Olympics]].<ref name="sports-reference">{{cite web |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ah/antonio-ahumada-1.html |title=Antonio Ahumada Olympic Results |accessdate=2010-06-11 |work=sports-reference.com}}</ref>
