===Actual usage in names=== Usage of the Jinmeiyō Kanji in Japanese names varies widely. For example, 之, is used in over 6000 names, and the 53 kanji used most commonly in names are all in over 500 names each.<ref name=kanshudo>Kanshudo, [https://www.kanshudo.com/collections/jinmeiyo_kanji The Jinmeiyō Kanji (人名用漢字)]</ref>
