'''Mario Lambrughi''' (born 5 February 1992) is an [[Italy|Italian]] male [[400 metres hurdles|hurdler]]. In 2018, establishing her [[Personal record|Personal Best]] with 48.99, at 13 May 2018 had reached the 1st place in the seasonal European lists.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fidal.it/content/Tortu-la-prima-%C3%A8-da-10-16-exploit-Lambrughi-48-99/114121|title=Tortu: la prima è da 10.16, exploit Lambrughi 48.99|publisher=fidal.it|accessdate=14 May 2018}}</ref>
