'''Tereza Chlebovská''' (born December 10, 1990)  is a [[Czechs|Czech]] model and beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned [[Czech Miss|Česká Miss 2012]] and was represented her [[Czech Republic|country]] in the 2012 [[Miss Universe 2011|Miss Universe]] pageant. She was unplaced there.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://globalbeauties.com/blog/2012/03/ceska-miss-2012/ |title=Ceska Miss 2012 |publisher=Global Beauties |date=2012-03-31 |accessdate=2012-04-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120402191100/http://globalbeauties.com/blog/2012/03/ceska-miss-2012/ |archivedate=2012-04-02 |df= }}</ref>

==Early life==
Tereza was studying at the [[University of Ostrava]]. She interrupted study after the competition.

==Česká Miss 2012==
Tereza Chlebovská was crowned "Česká Miss 2012" at the Grand Finale of Česká Miss 2012 beauty contest on Saturday night, 31 March 2012 at the Karlín Musical Theatre.

==Personal life==

Chlebovská is married with Czech footballer [[Pavel Kadeřábek]] who currently plays for [[TSG 1899 Hoffenheim|1899 Hoffenheim]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://revue.idnes.cz/tereza-chlebovska-priznala-vztah-s-fotbalistou-pavlem-kaderabkem-p9y-/sex.aspx?c=A140528_122515_sex_nh|title=Chlebovská už přítele netají, je to fotbalista Pavel Kadeřábek|language=Czech|last=Herrmannová|first=Nela |work=Mladá fronta DNES|date=28 May 2014|accessdate=30 May 2014}}</ref>

